Package com.googlecode.prmf.merapi.util

Various utility classes.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Filter<T> Defines an operation for deciding whether or not to "keep" objects.
Mapper<T,U> Defines a function (in the mathematical sense) for manipulating objects.
 

Class Summary
Arrays Various methods for manipulating arrays.
CharacterMapper<T> Maps objects onto characters.
CharSequenceList<T> Interprets a List as a CharSequence.
CloneableObject An alternative to implementing Cloneable for cloneable objects.
DelegatingList<T> A list that delegates its list-related methods to another list.
DelegatingMap<K,V> A map that delegates its map-related methods to another map.
Iterators Utility methods for manipulating iterators and iterable structures.
Pair<T,U> Groups two values in an immutable pair.
Quadruple<T,U,V,W> Groups four values in an immutable quadruple.
Streams Utility methods for manipulating streams and "streamable" objects.
Strings A collection of string-related utilities.
Triple<T,U,V> Groups three values in an immutable triple.
Wrapper<T> Holds a value.
